  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Want to experience the fun of rapidly expanding your territory? Then come and play this \"Quick Territory Expansion\" game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459810/extras/1e170ad9da2a9bc1af3e4184974ebcb4.avif?t=1745731606\" width=150 height=150 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459810/extras/4d1e6077241c151214b56a627ca507ae.avif?t=1745731606\" width=150 height=161 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459810/extras/975edac45778667c8e545f891c5ac2d1.avif?t=1745731606\" width=150 height=164 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459810/extras/35eb8af0e1e0740b2a286fb60445b21f.avif?t=1745731606\" width=150 height=151 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Plan land resources</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Increase the amount of usable land by clearing forests or broadleaf forests.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adjacent farms and villages will generate more revenue.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459810/extras/dd3787a7e0f68e7116dff76d4bbe510b.avif?t=1745731606\" width=150 height=164 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459810/extras/6d3198d0453ed70fe17d739777dac2d0.avif?t=1745731606\" width=150 height=192 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459810/extras/76c329c4cfed492a65aacf07130bc386.avif?t=1745731606\" width=150 height=174 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459810/extras/208e2727163b54518af8ace6ff9696a7.avif?t=1745731606\" width=150 height=206 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Respond to internal kingdom challenges</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the game, a large population is both the foundation of the kingdom's strength and a challenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The population can be used for conscription or arranged for production.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Maintain the kingdom's ruling power through soldiers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ruling power is the basis for the stability and high output of the kingdom; the more population you have, the more soldiers you need to maintain the kingdom's ruling power.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Population, lack of housing, unemployed civilians, rioters, and high war weariness will all reduce the kingdom's ruling power.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459810/extras/d0eb6b222271a7e3d21956cedcdf9906.avif?t=1745731606\" width=150 height=196 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459810/extras/947f108c1341cffa9fb904d54a0eef54.avif?t=1745731606\" width=150 height=164 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459810/extras/4de17a363db0814123993a2d09039f7e.avif?t=1745731606\" width=150 height=207 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459810/extras/35538f7c65188f373cb715b493fc9267.avif?t=1745731606\" width=150 height=165 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Respond to external kingdom challenges</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build fortresses, barracks, and other defensive structures to fend off threats from neighboring kingdoms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >War brings great resource consumption; also, avoid losing too many soldiers, as this will disrupt the internal stability of the kingdom, leading to crises and even collapse.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Want to experience the fun of rapidly expanding your territory? Then come and play this \"Quick Territory Expansion\" game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459810/extras/1e170ad9da2a9bc1af3e4184974ebcb4.avif?t=1745731606\" width=150 height=150 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459810/extras/4d1e6077241c151214b56a627ca507ae.avif?t=1745731606\" width=150 height=161 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459810/extras/975edac45778667c8e545f891c5ac2d1.avif?t=1745731606\" width=150 height=164 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459810/extras/35eb8af0e1e0740b2a286fb60445b21f.avif?t=1745731606\" width=150 height=151 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Plan land resources</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Increase the amount of usable land by clearing forests or broadleaf forests.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adjacent farms and villages will generate more revenue.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459810/extras/dd3787a7e0f68e7116dff76d4bbe510b.avif?t=1745731606\" width=150 height=164 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459810/extras/6d3198d0453ed70fe17d739777dac2d0.avif?t=1745731606\" width=150 height=192 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459810/extras/76c329c4cfed492a65aacf07130bc386.avif?t=1745731606\" width=150 height=174 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459810/extras/208e2727163b54518af8ace6ff9696a7.avif?t=1745731606\" width=150 height=206 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Respond to internal kingdom challenges</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the game, a large population is both the foundation of the kingdom's strength and a challenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The population can be used for conscription or arranged for production.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Maintain the kingdom's ruling power through soldiers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ruling power is the basis for the stability and high output of the kingdom; the more population you have, the more soldiers you need to maintain the kingdom's ruling power.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Population, lack of housing, unemployed civilians, rioters, and high war weariness will all reduce the kingdom's ruling power.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459810/extras/d0eb6b222271a7e3d21956cedcdf9906.avif?t=1745731606\" width=150 height=196 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459810/extras/947f108c1341cffa9fb904d54a0eef54.avif?t=1745731606\" width=150 height=164 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459810/extras/4de17a363db0814123993a2d09039f7e.avif?t=1745731606\" width=150 height=207 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3459810/extras/35538f7c65188f373cb715b493fc9267.avif?t=1745731606\" width=150 height=165 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Respond to external kingdom challenges</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build fortresses, barracks, and other defensive structures to fend off threats from neighboring kingdoms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >War brings great resource consumption; also, avoid losing too many soldiers, as this will disrupt the internal stability of the kingdom, leading to crises and even collapse.</p>",
